		{
			"type": "action",
			"name": "Pheromone Aura",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "passive"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>20 Feet; @Check[will|dc:23]</p><hr /><p>Every living creature that start their turn within the Pheromone Aura must attempt a Will Save or be under one of the following effects for 1 round, chosen by the Kikimore Queen. Creatures who suceeds are unaffected for 24h from the Pheremone Aura.</p><hr /><ul><li><p><strong>Aggression</strong> the affected Creature becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.AdPVz7rbaVSRxHFg]{Fascinated} by the Queen and consider the Kikimore as allies until the start of their next turn. Fascinated creatures has a status bonus of +2 to hit against every creature that isn't at full Hit Points while under the effect. @UUID[Compendium.monster-homebrewery.effects.Item.2Zm3X0d3hst9EmIJ]{Effect: Kikimore Queen's Aggressive Pheromone}</p></li><li><p><strong>Threat</strong> the affected Creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened 1} (@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened 2} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.sDPxOjQ9kx2RZE8D]{Fleeing} with a critical failure).</p></li><li><p><strong>Pacify</strong> the affected Creature is considered @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.fBnFDH2MTzgFijKf]{Unconscious} until the end of its next turn while under this effect, but doesn't fall @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.j91X7x0XSomq8d60]{Prone} (the creature is also knocked prone if they critically fails).</p></li></ul><p></p>",
					"gm": ""
				},
